                    +b.typography 
                        p 
                            strong 
                                big Your friend sends the balance of USDT 10,000 to trade, and receives 59USDT every day. And you get an instant 1300 USDT, which are immediately available to output!
                        p If your friend invites  friends, you'll get 2% off their investment! You can find the invitation link in your personal account under Partner Program. Just copy it and send it to  friends.

                    +b.A(href="register.html" class="btn --yellow-gr")
                        span Invite your friend
                        +e.SPAN.icon-wrap
                            +icon('001-right-arrow')
                +e.col 
                    +e.media
                        img(src="assets/images/referral/pic.png", alt="")

